column2: I am capable of answering frequently asked questions such as the type of products we sell, the type of payment methods we offer, and more. You can also ask me for information about the company including our opening times, and location. To view the full list of questions, go to myvoicebot.co.uk. In case I am not able to answer your question, I can also escalate your call to a human.
Hi, I am the virtual assistant for myvoicebot. I will be acting as your guide and walk you through this demo call. To begin, try saying: 'What are you capable of?'.
I didn't hear you say anything, can you try saying it again?
I am sorry I couldn't find a response for your query, please try asking in a different way?
